[thinking] **Inspecting class coverage**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm wondering if Class.forName in class$ is optimized away or if the dynamic access tracker overlooks Class.forName when it comes to JDK classes. But there are many class$ calls from other classes that probably refer to custom classes rather than JDK ones. I think it might be worthwhile to look into the coverage of something like KaffeRmic.class$ to see if the coverage might be inaccurately reported. This could lead to some interesting findings!
[thinking] 
